    {
      "id": "4b16c7bc-a2f5-448e-9245-dac2b8c25d93_c2b27edc-aa94-4266-b8fc-9df822f563e4",
      "label": "What excites you about the opportunity to join Talos?",
      "type": "input_text",
      "required": true,
      "value": "I'm excited about the opportunity to work at Talos Trading because I'm drawn to organizations that operate at scale, solve complex technical challenges, and prioritize innovation and long-term impact. Throughout my experience at Microsoft and Amazon Robotics, I've enjoyed working at the intersection of technology, operations, and strategy — leading cross-functional initiatives, building scalable systems, and driving measurable business outcomes.\n\nWhat particularly interests me about Talos Trading is the opportunity to contribute to high-impact products and programs while collaborating with talented teams across engineering, product, and business functions. I'm especially motivated by environments where I can combine technical depth with program leadership to improve reliability, automation, and operational efficiency.\n\nIn my current role, I've led large-scale resilience and automation initiatives, developed AI-driven workflow solutions, and managed complex cross-organizational programs under executive visibility. I enjoy taking ambiguous problems, creating structure, and driving execution from concept through delivery. I'd be excited to bring that same mindset to Talos Trading while continuing to grow in a fast-paced and innovative environment.\n\nBeyond the technical challenges, I'm also looking for a company whose culture emphasizes ownership, collaboration, and continuous improvement. From what I've seen, Talos Trading aligns strongly with those values, which makes the opportunity especially compelling to me.",
